      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PET DETECTIVE (1) held his own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only a nose (19.54) behind Slick Angel at this track. Has a strong record out of this box with seven wins and four minor placings from 13 starts. Can measure up this time. GIN AND JUICE (6) is progressing well scoring last time out (16.70) at this track and bringing up his 12th career win. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Has put together a string of wins and expected to go close again. FLYING HUGO (8) boasts a strong record this journey with four wins and three minors from eight tries. Placed last time (19.72) at this track in a Grade 6, finishing second and beaten half a length. Looks one of the chances. MAKE SOME NOISE (2) won as favourite last time – cannot be taken lightly.",
